{"article_id":"RkTmlyuibcPLxHlP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Let 's begin with a verbatim quote from President Obama from July of 2009 ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"touting the legislative perfection","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that would be Obamacare :","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"\" If you like your doctor ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"you will be able to keep your doctor .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Period .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"If you like your health care plan ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"you will be able to keep your health care plan .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Period .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"No one will take it away .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"No matter what . \"","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Many people","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who buy their own health insurance","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"could get surprises in the mail this fall :","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"cancellation notices","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"because their current policies are n't up to the basic standards of President Barack Obama 's health care law .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"They , and some small businesses , will have to find replacement plans","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"- and that has some state insurance officials worried about consumer confusion .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Also , it does n't seem to square with one of the president 's best known promises about his health care overhaul :","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"`` If you like your health care plan ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"you 'll be able to keep your health care plan . '' ...","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"The Obama administration did not respond directly to questions about the potential fallout from cancellation notices ...","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"For the most part , state insurance commissioners are giving insurers the option","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"of canceling existing plans","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"or changing them","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"to comply with new federal requirements .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"`` Canceling '' and `` changing '' do not equal `` keeping , ''","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"which was the promise .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"The CBO estimated last year","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that up to 20 million Americans could lose their current coverage under Obamacare .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Other projections","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"you turn for help ?","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"If your instant reply was `` Nancy Pelosi , ''","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"you 're in luck .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Have fun","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"`` Canceling '' and `` changing '' do not equal `` keeping , ''","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"which was the promise .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"The CBO estimated last year","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that up to 20 million Americans could lose their current coverage under Obamacare .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Other projections peg the number at 35 million , or more .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"With the media focused on the administration 's myriad scandals ,","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"the president is gearing up for yet another public relations tour on behalf of the law","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"that he never sold to the public ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"despite delivering dozens of speeches .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"His new plan ?","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"More speeches , natch , plus plenty of taxpayer-funded propaganda .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"If your presidency were sagging beneath the weight of scandal ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"and your top legislative accomplishment remained enduringly unpopular with the public ,","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to whom wouldturn for help ?","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"If your instant reply was `` Nancy Pelosi , ''","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"you 're in luck .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"Have fun with this , Democrats :","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"A document","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"circulated to House Democrats by Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"- and obtained by BuzzFeed -","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"offers some details of the timing of the health-care plan :","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Rates and details of plans will become public in September for the 34 states","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that haven ' t put together their own plans .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"The goals ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Pelosi writes in a \" dear colleague \" letter","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that begins the document ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"are \" to educate our constituents about the new law ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"help to implement it ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and strengthen the hands of those","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"who have worked for this historic reform . \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Pelosi 's guide","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"to finally selling Obamacare","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"runs 78 pages long ,","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"which sounds a bit unwieldy","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"until you remember what they 're","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Pelosi 's guide to finally selling Obamacare runs 78 pages long ,","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"which sounds a bit unwieldy","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"until you remember what they 're trying to summarize","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"( while editing out all the bad news ) .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"But do n't panic , Democrats .","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"Follow your super-popular leader 's game plan ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"and everything should be fine .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"This unambiguous , clearly-stated pledge was demonstrably false","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"when it was first uttered","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"and has remained so to this day .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"The latest piece of evidence , via the","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"( headline :","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"`` Like Your Healthcare Policy ?","depth":10},